b'Chikan no Licence':
b'This is the Forbidden License! The bearer of this license is able to create a field within which any manner of indecent or immoral acts seem normal. It is the ultimate permit for licentiousness.

Within the confines of a train car, the girls have nowhere to run. At the moment when their resistance dies, their despair changes to pleasure...

Based on a game by Black Rainbow and C:drive.

(Source: AnimeNfo)'
